Kocin Lakers, Luke Walton, ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa ta farko da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma ba a yanke shawarar ko zai buga wasan ba har tsawon minti.
A shafin yanar gizon Lakers, Walton ya ce "Zai wuce minti 1 ko kasa da 48".
Mike Trudell, dan jaridar Lakers ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai buga wasa ne na iyakantaccen lokaci.
Bayan atisayen da suka yi a farkon wannan makon, an tambayi James game da jadawalin wasannin Lakers na kakar wasa ta farko.
Ya ce, "Babu bukatar wasannin kafin kakar wasa a wannan lokaci na shirin".
Trump lokacin taron na West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara gangamin da aka yi a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne taron farko na tarurruka biyar da shugaba Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda zai hada da taron da za a yi a Tennessee da Mississippi.
A yayin da aka samu kuri'un amincewa da cika kofin kotun koli, Trump ya yi niyyar gina goyon baya ga zaben da ke tafe, saboda yana cikin hadari cewa jam'iyyar Republican ba za ta iya mamaye majalisa ba idan aka yi zabe a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump na yammacin Virginia zai gudana, kuma yaya kuke kallon sa a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump na Wheeling a jihar West Virginia a karfe 7 na yammacin yau, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump na jihar West Virginia a YouTube a kai tsaye a ƙasa.
Trump zai yi magana a wannan makon game da sauraron wanda ya yi takarar babban alkalin kotun Burt Cavano, wanda ya yi taurin kai saboda zargin cewa yana da jima'i, yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike kan batun, wanda ya jinkirta zaben majalisar dattawa har mako guda.
Amma babban manufar wannan jerin tarurruka shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su sami wani matsayi a gaban zaben na watan Nuwamba.
Kamfanin Trump ya ce taron na biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa "yana da nufin karfafa masu aikin sa kai da magoya bayan jam'iyyar Republican da ke son karewa da kuma fadada manyan yankunan da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai", in ji Reuters.
Wani mai magana da yawun kamfen din Trump, wanda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa, ya shaida wa Reuters cewa, "Shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama a lokacin yakin neman zabe, saboda kula da majalisar dokoki na da matukar muhimmanci a cikin manufofinsa".
West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito cewa taron da za a yi a Wescvanco Arena a Wheeling a daren yau zai jawo masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh za su yi magana game da shi.
Wannan ne karo na biyu a cikin wata daya da Trump ya ziyarci jihar ta West Virginia, inda ya lashe zaben 2016 da kashi 40 cikin dari.
Trump yana neman taimakon dan takarar Sanata na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisy, wanda ya fadi a zabe.
Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia ya ce, "Sanin cewa shugaban kasa ya zo ne don ya yi zabe ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey".
