A shafi daya na "Sunday Morning" ranar 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka wuce, kuma a ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi na gaba Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
