HIV/AIDS: China ta sanar da cewa sabbin mutane sun karu da kashi 14 cikin 100
China ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suka ji rauni a kasar, in ji hukumar lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kawai, an samu sabbin mutane kusan 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun yadu ta hanyar jima'i, kuma wannan ya nuna cewa ba haka ba ne.
A al'adance, cutar HIV ta yadu cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin sakamakon kamuwa da jini.
Amma hukumar lafiya ta kasar Sin ta ce a wani taro a birnin Winan, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu da kusan rabin rabin.
Amma a kasar Sin, adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS na karuwa da mutum 100,000 a kowace shekara.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i na zama babban al'amari a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT.
Saboda dabi'u masu ra'ayin mazan jiya a kasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na mazajen da suka yi jima'i da maza za su yi aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna zuwa ne daga rashin isasshen kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan alaƙar.
Tun daga shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani mataki na magance matsalar.
