Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da cin zarafinsa da tallace-tallace
Jakadan Amurka ya zargi Beijing da amfani da kafofin watsa labarai na Amurka don yada farfagandar, mako guda bayan jaridar kasar Sin ta buga tallan shafi hudu a jaridar Amurka don amfanin juna na cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da Sin.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana game da tallafin da Chanaidaly ta biya bayan ya zargi China da son tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dattawa na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba a cikin jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a Iowa, Des Moines Register.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa China na son shiga cikin zaben Amurka ya tunatar da jami'an Amurka a wata hira da suka yi da kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters cewa Washington na neman sabon hanyar matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
Ko da yake yana da kyau gwamnatocin kasashen waje su yi talla don inganta kasuwanci, China da Amurka suna cikin yakin kasuwanci da ke kara tsanantawa inda suke ganin juna suna karbar haraji akan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su.
A farkon yakin cinikayya, ya ce harajin da China ke karba ya kasance ne don kai hari ga jihohin da ke fitar da kayayyaki kamar Iowa, wanda ya goyi bayan jam'iyyar Trump da kuma masana na China da Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka da kuma babban mai fitar da kayayyakin noma na kasar Sin, gwamnan Iowa, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
A cikin wata sanarwa da aka wallafa a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, Branstad ya rubuta cewa, "China ta ninka cin zarafi ta hanyar tura tallace-tallace ga 'yan jaridarmu masu 'yanci".
Branstad ya rubuta cewa, "Gwamnatin China tana amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin latsa da faɗar albarkacin baki ta hanyar yada farfagandar ta ta hanyar saka tallace-tallace a cikin littafin da ake kira "Destmoine Register".
Ya rubuta, "A akasin wannan, a cikin jaridu a nan Beijing, za ku ga ƙarancin muryoyin adawa, kuma ba za su iya ba da cikakken bayani game da ra'ayoyin da ake da su game da yanayin tattalin arziki na kasar Sin ba, saboda cewa kafofin watsa labarai suna cikin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin".
Ya kara da cewa, "ya guji buga labarin a wata jarida mai suna China", amma bai bayyana ko wace ce ba.
Masu sharhi sun gargadi 'yan mata masu matsakaicin ra'ayi da suka yi fice a gaban Kavanaugh Debacle
Yayin da manyan jami'an jam'iyyar Republican ke goyon bayan da kuma kare babban alkalin kotun Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zargi da cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za a fuskanci koma baya a zaben da ke tafe, musamman daga mata.
An yi ta ta nuna cewa yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun amince su yi zabe.
"Ba za a iya mayar da wannan ba", in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da majalisar ta wallafa ranar Asabar.
Leher ya ce yana shakkar cewa wannan babban hari na karshe kan binciken da FBI ke yi wa Jeff Flake, dan majalisar wakilai mai wakiltar Arizona, zai isa ya sa masu jefa kuri'a su yi fushi.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, ba za su manta da shi ba gobe, ba ma a watan Nuwamba ba", in ji jaridar Washington D.C., babban mai ba da shawara da kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar masu ci gaba MoveOn a ranar Juma'a.
A safiyar Juma'a, lokacin da jam'iyyar Republican da ke mulki a kwamitin shari'a ta yanke shawarar tilasta wa Kaverno yin nadin, duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, masu zanga-zanga sun shiga cikin shaidar a cikin zauren majalisar dattawa suna ihu, "Laraba na zuwa!"
"Himma da yaudara na jam'iyyar dimokradiyya sun fice daga cikin jerin sunayen masu shahara", in ji Stu Rothenberg, mai sharhi kan siyasa a shafin yanar gizo na labarai.
Kuma mutanen da suke da wannan ra'ayin sun ce sun riga sun samu adadi mai yawa:
Amma musamman a cikin mata masu jefa kuri'a a unguwannin da ba sa son shugaban kasa, amma ba sa yawan jefa kuri'a, da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a tsakanin shekara 18 zuwa 29".
Kafin Ford ya bayyana a fili zarginsa na cin zarafin dan takarar babban alkalin, an yi nazari kan cewa idan 'yan Republican suka yi watsi da amincewar, za a iya samun koma baya.
A cewar NBC News, Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin kasa na jam'iyyar Republican, ya ce a farkon makon da ya gabata, "wannan ya zama abin mamaki ga jam'iyyar Republican".
"Ba wai kawai game da kuri'ar kwamitin ba ne, ko kuma kuri'ar karshe, ko Cavernou za ta shiga cikin alkalan ba, amma game da yadda jam'iyyar Republican ta magance wannan batu da kuma yadda suka bi da ita", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan hukumar fifiko ta Amurka, kungiyar da ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat, a tashar labarai.
Amma bisa ga shaidar Ford da Caberno, jama'ar Amirka sun bambanta kan wanda ya kamata a yarda da shi.
Wani sabon binciken da aka yi a shafin YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun ce sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, ko kuma sun yi imani da shi, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun yi imani da shaidar Caverno.
Har ila yau, kashi 38 cikin 100 sun ce sun yi tunanin Cavernou ta yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake shaida, kuma kashi 30 cikin 100 sun ce ta yi ƙarya game da Ford.
Jaridar Guardian ta ruwaito cewa FBI tana binciken tuhumar da aka yi wa Ford da kuma akalla mai shigar da kara, Deborah Ramirez, bayan binciken da aka yi wa Flake.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ya shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa cewa Cavernough ya yi mata fyade lokacin da ta ke 'yar shekara 17.
Ramirez ta yi ikirarin cewa dan takarar babban kotu ya fallasa mata al'aurarsa a lokacin da yake halartar wani biki a lokacin da yake karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Fara sabon Intanet don sayen Google da Facebook, waɗanda suka kafa shirin yanar gizo na duniya
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, yana fara sabon kamfani don gasa da Facebook, Amazon, da Google.
Sabon aikin wannan almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ya dogara da dandamali mai buɗewa na Solid na Burns Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanne mutane za su iya samun damar yin amfani da su.
A wata hira da aka yi da kamfanin Fast, Burns Lee ya yi barkwanci cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
Ya ce game da sabon kamfanin, "Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu.
"Lokaci ne na tarihi".
Wannan app yana amfani da fasahar Solid don ba mutane damar gina nasu "kayan ajiyar bayanan kan layi" ko POD.
Wannan zai iya haɗawa da jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyuka, gudanar da jadawalin, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna cikin wannan browser a lokaci guda.
Abu na musamman game da ajiyar bayanan sirri na kan layi shine cewa kowane irin bayanai da za a iya samun damar su ya dogara ne akan mai amfani.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "samarwa ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar John Bruce, Shugaba na kamfanin, manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da albarkatu, aiyuka da fasaha da suka dace don taimakawa kowa ya sami damar amfani da kayayyakin Solid.
Kamfanin yanzu ya ƙunshi dandamali na tsaro wanda Berners-Lee, Bruce, da IBM suka saya, wasu masu haɓaka a kan layi waɗanda suka yi yarjejeniya don aiki a kan wannan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen su na rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Burns Lee da tawagarsa sun ce ba su yi magana da Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su iya kawo sauyi na gaba daya da za su inganta dukkan tsarin kasuwancin su cikin dare.
"Ba ma neman izinin su".
A cikin wata kasida a cikin Medium a ranar Asabar, Burns Lee ya rubuta cewa, manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu da zai taimaka wajen kare mutunci da ingancin sabon yanar gizo da aka gina akan Solid.
A 1994, Burns Lee ya sauya Intanet ta hanyar kafa World Wide Web Consortium a MIT.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Burns Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki.
Ko da lokacin da ya fara Inrupt, Burns Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma shugaban World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo, da kuma Cibiyar Nazarin Bayanai na Budewa.
